metadata.name: Vampire Mara Black Serpent
metadata.description:
In gloomy Transylvania, high in the mountains, is the castle of Dracula, in which his heirs, vampires and werewolves live.

Home in the family - Mara, vampire Black Serpent, great-granddaughter of Count Dracula.

She is strong, reserved and very beautiful. Ruthless in battle, protector of her vampire family. She is 700 years old. She leads the vampires in Dracula's family.
